373
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:48,200
Xun, hurry up.

374
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,000
Sorry. Sorry.

375
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:04,680
It's fine.

376
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:07,960
Thank you.

377
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,720
