398
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:25,359
Debt collectors?

399
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:27,340
♪I, Min♪

400
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:28,559
Don't move.

401
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:29,559
Stay put.

402
00:21:31,464 --> 00:21:32,839
