403
00:21:32,839 --> 00:21:34,279
You scoundrels!

404
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:36,039
Playing debt collectors?

405
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:38,000
Do you know who he is?

406
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,319
My boss.

407
00:21:41,279 --> 00:21:43,480
Be good and scram.

408
00:21:44,079 --> 00:21:46,319
Or we'll plant you all here.

409
00:21:46,319 --> 00:21:47,336
♪No need to worry♪

410
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:50,839
Mr. Wang, you okay?

411
00:21:52,008 --> 00:21:53,480
♪My family♪

412
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:56,480
I don't want to do this crappy job
for one more day.

413
00:21:59,559 --> 00:22:00,960
No one has any manners anymore.

414
00:22:12,519 --> 00:22:13,359
Come on.

