434
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:58,119
Tomorrow you'll be a model student.

435
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,480
Don't embarrass me.

436
00:23:01,279 --> 00:23:02,039
Xin

437
00:23:02,039 --> 00:23:03,559
