486
00:27:55,599 --> 00:27:56,160
Understood.

487
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:57,480
The moment he shows up,

488
00:27:57,480 --> 00:27:58,319
I'll make him pay.

489
00:27:58,680 --> 00:27:59,319
Qiang,

490
00:27:59,599 --> 00:28:00,920
