get him beaten up.

495
00:28:14,279 --> 00:28:15,319
Li Chadong,

496
00:28:19,759 --> 00:28:20,880
don't think having

497
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,519
a few tough kids under you

498
00:28:22,839 --> 00:28:24,039
makes you important again.

499
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,039
Without me,

500
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:28,440
