537
00:30:20,759 --> 00:30:22,279
Shen Xiaojun, go back to your seat.

538
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,119
Senior year starts today.

539
00:30:28,119 --> 00:30:29,480
New semester, fresh start.

540
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:31,319
