542
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:34,400
Come in.

543
00:30:38,799 --> 00:30:39,200
Come back.

544
00:30:41,279 --> 00:30:42,279
Introduce yourself.

545
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,279
My name is

546
00:30:53,599 --> 00:30:54,440
Tang Yixun.

547
00:30:55,039 --> 00:30:56,359
Welcome, Tang Yixun.

548
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,920
Sit in the last row. Textbook.

549
00:31:10,039 --> 00:31:10,799
Ye Haitang,

550
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:13,599
