576
00:32:37,319 --> 00:32:38,480
I live there.

577
00:32:39,279 --> 00:32:40,519
Know Qiang from Old Street?

578
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:43,960
No.

579
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:45,839
I'm Shen Xiaojun.

