00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,599
Come to me if you need anything.

581
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:49,519
His older brother works with Qiang.

582
00:32:49,799 --> 00:32:51,079
He's got connections there.

583
00:32:51,279 --> 00:32:52,079
Got it.

584
00:32:53,119 --> 00:32:53,920
Do you play ball?

585
00:32:54,079 --> 00:32:54,960
Let's play for a bit.

586
00:32:55,759 --> 00:32:56,359
I need to go.

587
00:32:56,359 --> 00:32:56,920
Next time.

588
00:33:07,119 --> 00:33:08,480
He's so pretentious.

589
00:33:09,119 --> 00:33:10,799
Where could he possibly need to go?

590
00:33:12,872 --> 00:33:17,960
(Meiwan High School of Fu'an County)

591
00:33:30,359 --> 00:33:31,759
- What's this?
- Return the money.

592
00:33:31,759 --> 00:33:33,079
Or I'll call the police.

593
00:33:35,759 --> 00:33:36,424
I don't have it.

594
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:37,880
You're in cahoots.

595
00:33:38,119 --> 00:33:39,656
You won't escape if I call the police.

596
00:33:43,079 --> 00:33:44,079
Your dad owes money.

597
00:33:44,839 --> 00:33:47,160
And debts must be paid, you know?

598
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:47,960
If you don't pay,

599
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:49,279
I'll report to the school

600
00:33:49,400 --> 00:33:50,440
that you robbed me.

601
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,799
Your schooling will be over.

602
00:33:52,359 --> 00:33:53,359
Go ahead then.

603
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,039
It was my grandma's.

604
00:33:55,039 --> 00:33:56,039
You have to return it.

605
00:33:58,640 --> 00:33:59,200
Tang.

606
00:34:05,799 --> 00:34:07,160
If your dad had paid his debt,

607
00:34:09,039 --> 00:34:10,240
nothing would've happened.

608
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:19,000
What did he say?

609
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,800
Just asked about the schedule.

610
00:34:21,719 --> 00:34:22,360
By the way,

611
00:34:22,559 --> 00:34:23,920
we heard he's a hooligan.

612
00:34:24,159 --> 00:34:26,239
Zhou Peng saw him
at the Old Street pool hall.

613
00:34:26,639 --> 00:34:27,760
Doesn't look like one.

614
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:30,440
I don't go to Old Street much.

615
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,320
Just keep your distance.

616
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:39,272
(Sunshine Bookstore)

617
00:34:53,501 --> 00:34:56,681
(Your wishes will shine into reality
like the northern lights.)

618
00:35:02,159 --> 00:35:02,719
Sir.

619
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:05,519
These mosquitoes are vicious.

620
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:09,480
Tang,

621
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,320
here's your last month's wages.

622
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,199
Count it.

623
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:15,079
Thank you, sir.

624
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:15,519
No problem.

625
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,800
Since we've

626
00:35:18,159 --> 00:35:19,800
stocked new postcards

627
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:21,119
and stationery supplies recently,

628
00:35:21,639 --> 00:35:23,119
my wife wants to run an event.

629
00:35:23,119 --> 00:35:24,079
Can you organize it?

630
00:35:25,239 --> 00:35:26,159
What kind of event?

631
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:27,519
Something like

632
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:28,880
writing to your future self

633
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,280
to share thoughts.

634
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,079
So you can read it

635
00:35:31,079 --> 00:35:32,159
to revisit those thoughts.

636
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:33,199
Okay.

637
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:34,639
Refine the idea.

638
00:35:34,639 --> 00:35:35,800
Think of a catchy title.

639
00:35:36,719 --> 00:35:37,480
I'm on it.

640
00:35:49,159 --> 00:35:49,920
Cha,

641
00:35:50,599 --> 00:35:51,519
got any work today?

642
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:53,280
You're in school now.

643
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,280
Can you still do it?

644
00:35:55,079 --> 00:35:55,840
I can.

645
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,320
Alright.

646
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:00,760
Let's go to the dock.

647
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:01,599
Okay.

648
00:36:07,269 --> 00:36:10,000
(Art Design)

649
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:10,760
Tang.

650
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,280
Take these cardboard boxes

651
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:15,400
to sell yourself later.

652
00:36:16,679 --> 00:36:17,480
Thank you, sir.

653
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:17,800
Sure.

654
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:18,639
Take a look.

655
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:20,639
You're done?

656
00:36:21,719 --> 00:36:23,480
Write a letter to your future self.

657
00:36:23,719 --> 00:36:24,599
The title's good.

658
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,280
When people write letters,

659
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:27,519
how should we handle them?

660
00:36:27,519 --> 00:36:28,639
Should we mail them?

661
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,119
We're just running an event.

662
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:32,320
Our main goal is to sell products.

663
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:33,760
My wife learned this

664
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,079
from people in the city.

665
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:37,079
Consider it like writing a diary.

666
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,280
So it's fake.

667
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,880
You're missing the point.

668
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,480
What's a diary's purpose?

669
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:44,320
To express feelings, right?

670
00:36:44,639 --> 00:36:45,800
The feelings are genuine.

671
00:36:46,519 --> 00:36:47,599
And we'll properly

672
00:36:47,599 --> 00:36:48,920
store the letters.

673
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:50,119
They can view or retrieve them

674
00:36:50,119 --> 00:36:51,039
anytime.

675
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:53,119
I'll write one.

676
00:36:53,199 --> 00:36:53,760
And you too.

677
00:36:54,079 --> 00:36:54,400
Okay.

678
00:36:54,679 --> 00:36:56,800
For those postcards, stationery,
and envelopes,

679
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:57,960
take whatever you like.

680
00:36:58,440 --> 00:36:58,840
Alright?

681
00:36:59,239 --> 00:37:00,960
I'm picking up Hu. See you later.

682
00:37:01,159 --> 00:37:01,880
Thank you, sir.

683
00:37:12,104 --> 00:37:14,472
(Sunshine Bookstore)

684
00:37:15,199 --> 00:37:15,760
Miss.

685
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:17,719
Miss.

686
00:37:18,639 --> 00:37:20,159
You don't need the cardboards, right?

687
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,639
Do you take cardboards?

688
00:37:24,079 --> 00:37:24,599
Can...

689
00:37:25,679 --> 00:37:26,880
can you give them to me?

690
00:37:28,519 --> 00:37:30,079
Fine, you can have them.

691
00:37:30,639 --> 00:37:31,320
Great, thanks.

692
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:32,960
I'll put them on your cart.

693
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:33,920
Okay.

694
00:37:34,599 --> 00:37:35,400
Thank you.

695
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:40,920
Thank you.

696
00:37:41,079 --> 00:37:41,679
No worries.

697
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:49,199
Thank you.

698
00:37:49,199 --> 00:37:49,760
No worries.

699
00:38:11,197 --> 00:38:15,848
(Buddies Billiards)

700
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:20,880
It was tough.

701
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:22,320
You were quick-witted.

702
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:23,360
Or he would've escaped.

703
00:38:23,599 --> 00:38:24,440
You okay, Xun?

704
00:38:24,599 --> 00:38:25,119
I'm fine.

705
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:36,760
You know what?

706
00:38:37,079 --> 00:38:38,800
The guy we beat today with the mustache

707
00:38:39,119 --> 00:38:40,199
is from Bao's hometown.

708
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:41,960
You think he'll tell Bao?

709
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:43,920
Bao wouldn't have given us the IOU

710
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,639
if he actually cared.

711
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,280
But if Bao finds out

712
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,840
we beat that guy up like that,

713
00:38:49,199 --> 00:38:50,719
he might get pissed.

714
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,719
So what?

715
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:53,000
Our job was never about

716
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:53,880
being polite.

717
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:54,960
I did the math.

718
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,480
In at most one month,

719
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:57,960
we can buy a boat.

720
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:00,440
A ten-meter trawler that can sail

721
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,039
at least 50 nautical miles.

722
00:39:02,639 --> 00:39:04,320
Then we'll leave
this crap business to Bao

723
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:06,000
and make some decent money.

724
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:07,360
Awesome.

725
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:10,400
I've hated those guys for ages.

726
00:39:10,719 --> 00:39:11,760
Then we can transport

727
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,320
something like clothing or stuff.

728
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,960
We'll make a thousand per trip.

729
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:15,360
Nice.

730
00:39:15,559 --> 00:39:16,480
But won't Bao think

731
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,639
we're stealing his business?

732
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,079
He's got people

733
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,400
working on boats too.

734
00:39:20,679 --> 00:39:21,519
Don't forget.

735
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:23,320
We'll run a legitimate business.

736
00:39:23,679 --> 00:39:25,119
Bao doesn't own the sea.

737
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,800
If he does 1,000, I'll do 800.

738
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:27,960
If he does 800, I'll do 500.

739
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:29,159
So what if we undercut him?

740
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:30,679
I'll even do 300.

741
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,320
Come on.

742
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:39,760
By the way,

743
00:39:40,599 --> 00:39:42,360
forget about Ye Yibo's uncollected debt.

744
00:39:48,639 --> 00:39:49,320
Why?

745
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,119
Nothing particular.

746
00:39:50,519 --> 00:39:52,199
Let Bao's men handle those small jobs.

747
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:53,440
We only take big deals.

748
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:55,639
Then Ye Yibo's daughter will suffer.

749
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:58,119
Bao's crew collects debts
with brutal methods.

750
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:01,159
A bunch of scumbags.

751
00:40:19,159 --> 00:40:20,079
Good morning, sir.

752
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:20,840
Morning.

753
00:40:23,599 --> 00:40:25,159
Where did this mailbox come from?

754
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:26,000
No idea.

755
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:27,199
No idea who left it.

756
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:29,119
Right.

757
00:40:29,599 --> 00:40:30,639
It has a letter for you.

758
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:31,440
For me?

759
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:32,480
Yes.

760
00:40:32,800 --> 00:40:33,760
I found it inside it.

761
00:40:34,239 --> 00:40:35,360
Who'd write me a letter?

762
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:36,840
(To Ye Haitang)
No idea.

763
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:37,760
Who did this?

764
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:39,840
Why did they put a crappy mailbox

765
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:40,639
before my shop?

766
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:42,920
Thank you.

767
00:40:43,159 --> 00:40:43,920
No worries.

768
00:40:52,119 --> 00:40:53,320
We're running an event.

769
00:40:54,199 --> 00:40:55,119
This mailbox can help.

770
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:57,079
We can have people put the letters here.

771
00:40:57,760 --> 00:40:58,239
Okay then.

772
00:40:58,239 --> 00:40:59,079
You go get a lock.

773
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,119
Lock this up.

774
00:41:00,119 --> 00:41:00,559
I...

775
00:41:00,559 --> 00:41:01,119
The school.

776
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:02,000
I'll get it.

777
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:02,800
You go to school.

778
00:41:34,717 --> 00:41:37,832
(Meiwan High School of Fu'an County)

779
00:41:57,119 --> 00:41:59,039
Didn't we just pay this last semester?

780
00:41:59,039 --> 00:42:00,000
Why are we paying again?

781
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,159
Miss Tan decides class fund usage.

782
00:42:02,159 --> 00:42:03,639
Go to her if you have issues.

783
00:42:04,239 --> 00:42:04,800
Wow.

784
00:42:05,199 --> 00:42:07,119
You're really her pet.

785
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:08,679
So you're the class monitor.

786
00:42:09,039 --> 00:42:10,880
Do you get a cut from the class fund?

787
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:11,920
Three yuan for class fund.

788
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:13,719
Fine, monitor.

789
00:42:14,119 --> 00:42:14,679
How about

790
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:16,920
I give you ten yuan,

791
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:18,239
and you make me vice monitor?

792
00:42:19,159 --> 00:42:20,119
Here's your seven yuan.

793
00:42:20,519 --> 00:42:22,400
Ask the teachers
about becoming the monitor.

794
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:24,960
She gave you seven yuan.

795
00:42:24,960 --> 00:42:26,199
Does that mean a 'no'?

796
00:42:26,519 --> 00:42:27,880
Why are you so nosy?

797
00:42:34,519 --> 00:42:35,559
Three yuan for class fund.

798
00:42:50,719 --> 00:42:51,800
Come out.

799
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:08,960
What are you doing?

800
00:43:09,239 --> 00:43:09,800
Unlike you,

801
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:11,239
Ye Haitang surely did her homework.

802
00:43:11,599 --> 00:43:13,719
Stop messing with her belongings.

803
00:43:13,719 --> 00:43:15,360
What's wrong
with studying her math paper?

804
00:43:15,719 --> 00:43:17,320
Shen Xiaojun, why are you so annoying?

805
00:43:17,519 --> 00:43:18,880
She'll scold you when she's back.

806
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:19,719
I don't fear her.

807
00:43:28,719 --> 00:43:29,360
What?

808
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:31,800
I'm warning you.

809
00:43:32,559 --> 00:43:33,599
Don't think

810
00:43:33,599 --> 00:43:34,800
you can bully me freely.

811
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:37,239
If you write me that stuff again,

812
00:43:37,239 --> 00:43:38,000
I'll just

813
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:38,880
call the police.

814
00:43:39,239 --> 00:43:40,719
What did I write?

815
00:43:40,960 --> 00:43:41,880
What are you saying?

816
00:43:43,639 --> 00:43:44,760
I'm not afraid of you guys.

817
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:49,320
Explain yourself clearly.

818
00:43:52,599 --> 00:43:53,599
Tang,

819
00:43:53,800 --> 00:43:56,960
we're both people
who crawled out of the muddy pit.

820
00:43:57,239 --> 00:43:59,320
No one understands better than us

821
00:43:59,519 --> 00:44:02,079
how pathetic and insignificant we were.

822
00:44:04,400 --> 00:44:05,280
Stop laughing.

823
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:06,960
The next part's even cornier.

824
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,280
I can't even read it aloud.

825
00:44:08,400 --> 00:44:11,880
Tang, no matter how much time passes,

826
00:44:11,880 --> 00:44:14,920
I still deeply yearn for you.

827
00:44:14,920 --> 00:44:16,840
I've never forgotten

828
00:44:16,840 --> 00:44:17,679
our time together.

829
00:44:17,679 --> 00:44:18,280
Shen Xiaojun!

830
00:44:23,440 --> 00:44:24,400
Give it back!

831
00:44:26,719 --> 00:44:31,000
Tang, I'll never forget you.

832
00:44:31,119 --> 00:44:32,719
Xun.

833
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:35,800
Who's Xun?

834
00:44:35,800 --> 00:44:37,559
You can guess.

835
00:44:38,119 --> 00:44:40,119
Look, Xun's here.

836
00:44:40,840 --> 00:44:44,719
- Xun!
- Xun!

837
00:44:47,559 --> 00:44:48,840
Why did you kick me?

838
00:44:54,679 --> 00:44:55,400
What is this?

839
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:57,800
Tang Yixun, can't you read?

840
00:44:57,800 --> 00:44:58,960
You wrote this love letter.

841
00:44:58,960 --> 00:45:00,000
Don't you know?

842
00:45:01,519 --> 00:45:02,519
Don't tear it.

843
00:45:02,519 --> 00:45:03,440
Are you feeling shy?

844
00:45:03,559 --> 00:45:04,599
What are you doing?

845
00:45:09,559 --> 00:45:10,440
Tang Yixun,

846
00:45:11,159 --> 00:45:12,239
you came here days ago.

847
00:45:12,239 --> 00:45:13,599
What did you promise me?

848
00:45:13,840 --> 00:45:14,840
I didn't write it.

849
00:45:15,280 --> 00:45:16,000
Then who did?

850
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:16,960
How would I know?

851
00:45:17,239 --> 00:45:18,440
I definitely didn't write it.

852
00:45:19,400 --> 00:45:20,119
Tang, you speak.

853
00:45:20,559 --> 00:45:22,000
Don't be afraid. Just say the truth.

854
00:45:23,280 --> 00:45:24,559
He gave it to you, didn't he?

855
00:45:26,280 --> 00:45:27,119
Explain quickly.

856
00:45:27,119 --> 00:45:28,000
Hand off. Stand still!

857
00:45:29,840 --> 00:45:31,079
Say something!

858
00:45:31,079 --> 00:45:31,719
Tell her

859
00:45:31,719 --> 00:45:33,079
who wrote this to you.

860
00:45:37,119 --> 00:45:38,000
You go back first.

861
00:45:46,639 --> 00:45:47,519
Tang Yixun,

862
00:45:48,320 --> 00:45:50,119
I enrolled you here to study,

863
00:45:50,280 --> 00:45:52,440
not to get involved in this nonsense.

864
00:45:52,440 --> 00:45:53,280
I didn't do it.

865
00:45:54,320 --> 00:45:55,079
Isn't this

866
00:45:55,639 --> 00:45:56,559
your handwriting?

867
00:45:57,199 --> 00:45:58,440
The writing looks like mine.

868
00:45:58,639 --> 00:45:59,440
But I didn't do it.

869
00:45:59,559 --> 00:46:00,000
You didn't?

