00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:00,960
Then who did? Me?

871
00:46:01,320 --> 00:46:02,519
What other 'Xun' is there?

872
00:46:03,199 --> 00:46:04,559
Still refusing to admit it?

873
00:46:05,519 --> 00:46:07,280
When did you become like this?

874
00:46:09,000 --> 00:46:10,320
Go and write a self-criticism.

875
00:46:10,440 --> 00:46:11,400
I won't write it.

876
00:46:11,760 --> 00:46:13,400
I didn't write this letter.

877
00:46:14,719 --> 00:46:15,559
Why self-criticism?

878
00:46:19,709 --> 00:46:21,519
(Zihua Pavilion)

879
00:46:21,519 --> 00:46:22,159
Class dismissed.

880
00:46:22,400 --> 00:46:22,880
Stand up.

881
00:46:23,760 --> 00:46:26,639
Goodbye, sir.

882
00:46:26,760 --> 00:46:27,440
Goodbye.

883
00:46:30,039 --> 00:46:30,719
Leaving first.

884
00:46:31,559 --> 00:46:32,159
Bye.

885
00:47:00,880 --> 00:47:01,719
What are you doing?

886
00:47:02,079 --> 00:47:03,320
Where did the letter come from?

887
00:47:03,719 --> 00:47:04,719
Ye Haitang's backpack.

888
00:47:04,880 --> 00:47:05,960
Did you do this?

889
00:47:06,360 --> 00:47:07,079
It wasn't me.

890
00:47:07,079 --> 00:47:08,320
Your name was on it.

891
00:47:08,719 --> 00:47:10,440
Besides, I can't write that well.

892
00:47:13,639 --> 00:47:14,519
Listen to me.

893
00:47:15,519 --> 00:47:17,559
If I find out you're involved in this,

894
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:20,440
I'll break your arm.

895
00:47:22,440 --> 00:47:22,880
Tang Yixun,

896
00:47:24,639 --> 00:47:25,719
what are you doing?

897
00:47:26,639 --> 00:47:27,079
Let go.

898
00:47:32,719 --> 00:47:33,519
Let go.

899
00:47:34,000 --> 00:47:34,840
Let go!

900
00:47:45,519 --> 00:47:46,880
When I arrived at noon today,

901
00:47:46,880 --> 00:47:49,199
I heard several parents
discussing this matter.

902
00:47:50,760 --> 00:47:53,280
How could you
make such a mistake at school?

903
00:47:53,760 --> 00:47:56,199
Thankfully Miss Tan caught it in time.

904
00:47:57,320 --> 00:47:57,880
Tang,

905
00:47:58,519 --> 00:48:00,559
you've made me and Miss Tan worry.

906
00:48:01,880 --> 00:48:03,000
It isn't Tang's fault.

907
00:48:03,519 --> 00:48:04,840
As her homeroom teacher,

908
00:48:04,880 --> 00:48:05,880
I'm responsible too.

909
00:48:05,880 --> 00:48:06,599
No.

910
00:48:06,880 --> 00:48:09,199
The responsibility lies entirely
with me as her father.

911
00:48:09,559 --> 00:48:10,880
Because of my job,

912
00:48:10,880 --> 00:48:12,760
I've neglected Tang's upbringing.

913
00:48:13,199 --> 00:48:14,280
I've failed the school

914
00:48:14,400 --> 00:48:15,280
and failed her.

915
00:48:15,639 --> 00:48:16,880
Please don't say that.

916
00:48:17,079 --> 00:48:18,599
We're not here today to blame

917
00:48:18,599 --> 00:48:19,880
anyone for responsibility.

918
00:48:21,199 --> 00:48:23,199
Miss Tan, as you know,

919
00:48:23,519 --> 00:48:25,719
Tang's always been sensible.

920
00:48:26,960 --> 00:48:28,280
Her grandma's passing

921
00:48:28,679 --> 00:48:30,079
hit her very hard.

922
00:48:30,880 --> 00:48:32,960
And I've been away from home so long.

923
00:48:33,880 --> 00:48:36,079
Given their age,

924
00:48:36,320 --> 00:48:37,079
I believe

925
00:48:37,079 --> 00:48:39,239
they're just trying to make friends.

926
00:48:39,239 --> 00:48:40,000
Right.

927
00:48:40,000 --> 00:48:40,880
I hope you

928
00:48:40,880 --> 00:48:42,719
can give them a chance to correct this.

929
00:48:43,199 --> 00:48:45,079
I'll talk to her properly at home.

930
00:48:46,320 --> 00:48:48,320
This won't happen again.

931
00:48:48,320 --> 00:48:50,519
But please don't be hard on her.

932
00:48:50,519 --> 00:48:51,760
This really isn't Tang's fault.

933
00:48:52,280 --> 00:48:53,880
Senior year is stressful.

934
00:48:54,320 --> 00:48:56,079
And girls are more sensitive.

935
00:48:56,320 --> 00:48:58,079
She might need more attention at home.

936
00:48:58,400 --> 00:48:59,639
We appreciate your kindness.

937
00:48:59,639 --> 00:49:00,440
Not at all.

938
00:49:01,440 --> 00:49:02,480
So he is the...

939
00:49:03,639 --> 00:49:04,639
the boy?

940
00:49:07,960 --> 00:49:08,760
Stand up.

941
00:49:10,639 --> 00:49:11,840
What's your name?

942
00:49:17,079 --> 00:49:18,440
His name is Tang Yixun.

943
00:49:22,960 --> 00:49:23,880
Tang.

944
00:49:25,760 --> 00:49:27,400
Look at you, such a fine young man.

945
00:49:27,519 --> 00:49:29,079
Focus on your studies.

946
00:49:29,320 --> 00:49:30,880
I'm not against you making friends,

947
00:49:31,000 --> 00:49:32,960
but don't let this
affect your schoolwork.

948
00:49:33,199 --> 00:49:34,559
And you mustn't do anything

949
00:49:34,559 --> 00:49:35,960
that goes against student ethics.

950
00:49:36,559 --> 00:49:37,440
Don't you agree?

951
00:49:39,519 --> 00:49:41,079
Who are you to lecture me?

952
00:49:42,519 --> 00:49:43,559
And that letter

953
00:49:44,320 --> 00:49:45,360
has nothing to do with me.

954
00:49:45,639 --> 00:49:46,440
Tang Yixun!

955
00:49:46,880 --> 00:49:47,880
Miss Tan.

956
00:49:48,199 --> 00:49:50,280
Haven't we already settled this matter?

957
00:49:50,440 --> 00:49:52,280
I'm not trying to give you a hard time.

958
00:49:52,639 --> 00:49:54,119
I just hope that this incident

959
00:49:54,559 --> 00:49:56,519
can be treated as a joke this time.

960
00:49:56,519 --> 00:49:57,719
But you have to promise me

961
00:49:58,519 --> 00:50:00,079
there absolutely

962
00:50:00,719 --> 00:50:02,079
won't be a next time.

963
00:50:06,440 --> 00:50:08,079
Don't worry. There won't be a next time.

964
00:50:10,199 --> 00:50:10,679
Miss Tan,

965
00:50:10,679 --> 00:50:11,960
where's that letter?

966
00:50:12,960 --> 00:50:13,960
It was a joke.

967
00:50:13,960 --> 00:50:14,840
I've thrown it away.

968
00:50:15,480 --> 00:50:16,960
Let's just let this matter pass.

969
00:50:20,199 --> 00:50:22,199
Okay, let's drop it then.

970
00:50:22,719 --> 00:50:23,719
Thank you for coming.

971
00:50:23,719 --> 00:50:24,599
Let me walk you out.

972
00:50:25,079 --> 00:50:26,079
Alright.

973
00:50:28,559 --> 00:50:30,239
Let's go home, Tang.

974
00:50:50,880 --> 00:50:51,519
(Tang,)

975
00:50:52,880 --> 00:50:55,679
(I wanted to free you
from this endless suffering.)

976
00:50:56,960 --> 00:50:58,079
(But I never imagined)

977
00:50:59,000 --> 00:51:01,039
(I was opening another abyss.)

978
00:51:01,920 --> 00:51:04,039
(The abyss is worse than a pit.)

979
00:51:05,159 --> 00:51:06,280
(Because demons)

980
00:51:07,400 --> 00:51:08,679
(lurk in the abyss.)

